    "client_msg_id": "caa10684-0ecf-4800-9761-d90f6ed3134c",
    "text": "That's a great link. I think it would be cool if the shape (the way it's knitted) changes the behavior of the sensor. Measure electricity (static) directly? Then one could create software by knitting. Maybe it would look more like a Quipu (<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quipu>)..",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1713220604.752629",
    "parent_user_id": "UP00ZLX6G",
    "blocks": [
      {
